encePolicy\nmoved to the separate cache2k-addon module). It is used once, in\nDefaultPreheatCacheService.put() — whose cache path is currently disabled\n(isCacheEnabled() returns false), so the resilience setting protected a cache that\nis never built. Removing the call avoids pulling in the new cache2k-addon\ndependency for dead code.\n\nNo other source change is needed: every other cache2k API dhis2 uses\n(forUnknownTypes, eternal, expireAfterWrite(long,TimeUnit), entryCapacity, name,\npermitNullValues, build; Cache get/put/putIfAbsent/remove/removeAll/clear/keys/\nasMap/invoke + MutableCacheEntry.setExpiryTime) is unchanged in 2.6.1.Final, and\ndhis2 imports nothing from the removed org.cache2k.integration package.\n\nSupersedes dependabot #23778 (version-only, did not compile).\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) \u003cnoreply@anthropic.com\u003e","author":{"name":"Stian Sandvold","email":"stian@dhis2.org"},"id":"8acc269f6a445e020434a488e9e7c40839bd0e6c","tree_id":"13b22c7a2ff1eb0ba96bdf6b7f445938fdad1f8c","timestamp":"2026-06-02T11:45:47Z","committer":{"name":"Stian Sandvold","email":"stian@dhis2.org"}},"workflow_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/dhis2/dhis2-core/actions/workflows/5591308","repository":{"id":66940520,"node_id":"MDEwOlJlcG9zaXRvcnk2Njk0MDUyMA==","owner":{"login":"dhis2","id":1089987,"node_id":"MDEyOk9yZ2FuaXphdGlvbjEwODk5ODc=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/1089987?v=4","html_url":"https://github.com/dhis2","gravatar_id":"","type":"Organization","site_admin":false,"url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/events{/privacy}","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/following{/other_user}","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/followers","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/gists{/gist_id}","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/orgs","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/dhis2/received_events","re